om/v/t64.5771-25/38974518_1976302529467849_6152825660440571977_n.png?_nc_cat=101&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=3Tw9SkKM-1QQ7kNvgElXORr&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&_nc_gid=A6mbznVri_oaELetHbgZ0ge&oh=00_AYBGMueu4AMn_8zU1DcrE5k78OVnZrMIiQ_tkTUZGHixYQ&oe=66E80A78"}, "display_name": "Zen Monkeys", "keywords": ["zen", "monkey", "puzzle", "relax", "arcade"], "long_description": "The first rule of Zen is \"Do One Thing At A Time\". Zen Monkeys is a Zen-like playground to quiet your mind, relax, and hang. Build chains of Zen Monkeys in a peaceful and serene environment that is fun and calm.\n\nZen Monkeys is a simple straight forward experience in VR. A peaceful place to chill, climb, and hang.\n\nZen-Monkeys features:\n\nUnlimited Physics Based Zen Monkeys: Use as many as you'd like!\n\nA completely climbable set of Monkey Bars to hang your Zen Monkeys.\n\nDual-wield squirt guns to shoot down the chains you've created.\n\nAbility To Change The Monkey's Color\n\nMusic Selection Added\n\nCurrent DLC:\n\nLocking Monkey FREE DLC\n\nNew Space Environment DLC\n\nNew Open World \"The Islands\" DLC\n\nNew Open World \"Zen City\" with \"Zen Run\" mini-game DLC\n\nNew Open World \"Zen Archery\" with mini-games DLC\n\nZen Monkeys is a fun and relaxing getaway from school, work, chores or anything. So release your Zen!", "short_description": "The first rule of Zen is \"Do One Thing At A Time\".  Zen Monkeys is a Zen-like playground to quiet your mind, relax, and hang.  Build chains of Zen Monkeys in a peaceful and serene environment that is fun and calm."}]}, "developer_name": "John Ray Games", "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://johnray32875.wixsite.com/johnraygames/zen-monkeys", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "John Ray Games", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://johnray32875.wixsite.com/johnraygames", "category": "GAMES", "comfort_rating": "COMFORTABLE_FOR_SOME", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "co